but you may not get
out of your car to get it...

345
00:24:33,925 --> 00:24:36,844
"a bicycle, a vine and a dog."

346
00:24:36,845 --> 00:24:39,324
A dog?!

347
00:24:39,325 --> 00:24:40,924
A vine? A bicycle?

348
00:24:40,925 --> 00:24:45,244
Whereabouts on the Riviera
are you going to find...?
And a branch of a cedar tree...

349
00:24:45,245 --> 00:24:47,564
Oi! May!

350
00:24:47,565 --> 00:24:49,244
Yeah?

351
00:24:49,245 --> 00:24:53,164
What are you doing up there?
