372
00:26:16,165 --> 00:26:21,285
Operate the stereo from the
steering wheel, electric windows,
electric roof that opens. Ha-ha!

373
00:26:22,725 --> 00:26:27,004
Meanwhile, very far behind,
Captain Sense Of Direction

