381
00:26:58,885 --> 00:27:01,485
But I want this car to drive.

382
00:27:11,045 --> 00:27:16,605
Soon, we were in the hills
and ready to start our challenge.

383
00:27:17,925 --> 00:27:19,484
A bicycle, dog.

